alerts.description:
...WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM PDT SUNDAY...
* WHAT...North winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 45 mph.
* WHERE...Santa Clarita Valley, Eastern Santa Monica Mountains
Recreational Area, Western San Fernando Valley and Santa
Susana Mountains.
* WHEN...Until 9 AM PDT Sunday.
* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.
